WEBVTT

00:00.174 --> 00:05.122
♪ Hey, why is it happening ♪

00:06.094 --> 00:08.802
♪ My heart is racing ♪

00:09.934 --> 00:13.942
♪ The world has fallen silent ♪

00:13.966 --> 00:18.722
♪ Hey, when I imagine you ♪

00:19.758 --> 00:22.786
♪ What kind of look ♪

00:23.790 --> 00:27.734
♪ Attracted me to you ♪

00:27.758 --> 00:31.030
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:31.054 --> 00:34.518
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:34.542 --> 00:39.790
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:39.790 --> 00:41.408
♪ I love you ♪

00:41.408 --> 00:44.886
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:44.910 --> 00:48.182
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:48.206 --> 00:53.878
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:53.902 --> 00:55.246
♪ I love you ♪

00:55.246 --> 00:58.582
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:58.606 --> 01:01.954
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:02.062 --> 01:07.259
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:07.259 --> 01:08.942
♪ I love you ♪

01:08.942 --> 01:12.342
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

01:12.366 --> 01:15.766
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:15.790 --> 01:21.366
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:21.390 --> 01:24.802
♪ I love you ♪

01:27.080 --> 01:27.870
=Love Me, Love My Voice=

01:27.870 --> 01:31.070
=Love Me, Love My Voice=
=Episode 28=

01:31.070 --> 01:35.050
(What? You are one of my fans?)

01:35.074 --> 01:36.514
- Come in for cakes.
- Just waiting for you!

01:36.514 --> 01:37.654
They're here.

01:40.115 --> 01:44.535
- Congratulations to chief planner!
- The performance was a success!

01:44.915 --> 01:47.371
Thank you! Thanks to everyone!

01:47.395 --> 01:49.455
You've worked hard!
It was a fine performance.

01:51.475 --> 01:53.731
Just waiting for you.
It's time to cut the cake.

01:53.755 --> 01:55.055
Let him do the cutting.

01:55.835 --> 01:58.655
I know. I was just
passing the knife. Here!

01:59.794 --> 02:02.691
Zhou Zheng, as the director,
you've worked much harder.

02:02.715 --> 02:04.971
Anyway, Doudou's worked hard too.
She should do it.

02:04.995 --> 02:06.294
The chief planner.

02:07.114 --> 02:08.691
- You do it together.
- Alright.

02:08.715 --> 02:10.210
Perfect Voice
is the chief planner this year.

02:10.234 --> 02:12.210
And you are the founders.
You should do it together.

02:12.234 --> 02:16.514
- Together, together.
- Together.

02:16.514 --> 02:18.614
- One, two, three.
- One, two, three.

02:22.074 --> 02:24.291
- Come on, guys. Cakes for all of you.
- Give me plates.

02:24.315 --> 02:28.691
- Here!
- The devoted audience first.

02:28.715 --> 02:30.715
- Come on!
- Sheng!

02:30.715 --> 02:32.294
Xiaoxing, eat more.

02:33.195 --> 02:34.215
Thank you.

02:35.074 --> 02:37.330
- Have you checked Weibo?
- No.

02:37.354 --> 02:41.291
Look, many of his fans are limners.
They created many drawings for him.

02:41.315 --> 02:43.454
- And pictures about his retirement.
- Let me see.

02:44.562 --> 02:49.970
(Weibo of Qiang Qingci's fans)

02:50.794 --> 02:51.894
Really nice.

02:52.954 --> 02:55.330
- Guai, did you get any cake?
- It feels like being in the canteen.

02:55.354 --> 02:57.734
- Let me do it.
- Ma'am from a canteen.

03:02.514 --> 03:03.655
And this one.

03:04.068 --> 03:07.122
(Qiang Qingci, going further together.)

03:10.035 --> 03:13.810
Don't eat too much. After this,

03:13.834 --> 03:16.275
- let's find a place to have fun. Okay?
- Okay.

03:16.275 --> 03:18.210
- What'll it be?
- I'll post the address in the group.

03:18.234 --> 03:19.734
- Okay.
- Okay.

03:20.715 --> 03:22.014
Please!

03:27.514 --> 03:28.935
Help!

04:07.955 --> 04:09.335
When you finish,

04:10.194 --> 04:11.455
come with me to a place.

04:20.412 --> 04:23.475
(Traditional Music Gala)

04:23.475 --> 04:26.135
We're here. This is the place.

04:37.874 --> 04:40.215
- The audience's reaction was favorable.
- Right.

04:43.234 --> 04:44.415
Wait for me.

04:54.794 --> 04:56.015
Hello, everyone.

04:58.874 --> 05:02.575
Thank you very much
for your spectacular performance.

05:03.234 --> 05:05.504
- Thanks to you,
- Who is he?

05:05.504 --> 05:07.135
- we have a great performance.
- I don't know.

05:08.674 --> 05:10.614
I'm the chief planner of today's gala.

05:11.994 --> 05:14.054
- Qiang Qingci.
- Qiang Qingci?

05:14.314 --> 05:17.135
- Qiang Qingci?
- Mr. Qiang? Really?

05:20.434 --> 05:23.734
- Is he really the one?
- You've worked hard!

05:24.554 --> 05:28.410
Hello, Mr. Qiang. A few years ago,
I worked with you on an audio drama.

05:28.434 --> 05:30.290
I played your apprentice.
Do you remember?

05:30.314 --> 05:33.051
- Of course. Nice to meet you.
- Thank you, Mr. Qiang.

05:33.075 --> 05:35.170
- Keep going.
- No problem! Thank you!

05:35.194 --> 05:38.075
- I am particularly fond of you.
- May I have a photo taken with you?

05:38.075 --> 05:39.655
- Of course.
- All right.

05:42.595 --> 05:45.335
- Thank you.
- I'm one of your fans. I love your voice.

05:45.674 --> 05:48.415
- Alright!
- Looking good!

05:48.794 --> 05:51.210
- It's done.
- Send it to me.

05:51.234 --> 05:54.170
Come on, three, two, one, cheese!

05:54.194 --> 05:56.011
Thank you for your hard work.

05:56.035 --> 05:59.715
Mr. Qiang, you are my idol.
I entered this field because of you.

05:59.715 --> 06:01.655
You are my dream.

06:06.354 --> 06:09.650
(Because of him, countless people began
to pursue their dreams.)

06:09.950 --> 06:16.614
(Qiang Qingci is bound to be a name
that is hard to surpass and forget.)

06:19.874 --> 06:21.215
What a mess!

06:23.674 --> 06:26.011
- Still busy?
- Mr. Mo.

06:26.035 --> 06:27.854
- Mr. Wang Ke, Mr. Feishao.
- Thank you.

06:31.434 --> 06:33.015
Wait for me.

06:34.955 --> 06:37.254
Mr. Feishao, may I have this?

06:37.595 --> 06:40.415
- Just take whatever you want.
- Thank you.

06:43.515 --> 06:45.891
There're new ones in the studio.
I'll go back and get it for you.

06:45.915 --> 06:48.694
This carries special meaning.
I want this one.

06:49.874 --> 06:54.015
- You have to sign it for me.
- No problem.

06:59.314 --> 07:00.575
You're still here?

07:02.035 --> 07:05.215
We'll leave first.
We'll meet at the crossroads shortly.

07:06.035 --> 07:08.210
- See you later.
- Don't get exposed.

07:08.234 --> 07:08.850
- Let's go.
- Bye.

07:08.874 --> 07:10.011
- Bye.
- Bye.

07:10.035 --> 07:11.254
Bye.

07:12.314 --> 07:13.770
- Have you finished?
- Almost.

07:13.794 --> 07:15.051
- Just a minute.
- Just a minute.

07:15.075 --> 07:18.335
- Come on.
- Once you're done, give us a call.

07:18.794 --> 07:20.734
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

07:22.475 --> 07:23.854
Wang Ke.

07:25.155 --> 07:26.814
Wang Ke. He is Wang Ke.

07:28.994 --> 07:30.415
Wang Ke.

07:31.030 --> 07:33.580
♪ The wind listens to all the wishes ♪

07:33.580 --> 07:35.330
♪ Fluttering memories ♪

07:35.354 --> 07:39.535
- Take a rest. Be careful!
- Fighting! I love you!

07:39.994 --> 07:44.174
- Off Key is new. Please support him.
- Bye.

07:44.635 --> 07:46.770
- Be careful!
- Thank you.

07:46.794 --> 07:49.614
- Bye.
- Bye.

07:51.574 --> 07:54.130
♪ Then run towards the sunny day ♪

07:56.554 --> 07:58.775
What a large number of fans!

07:59.475 --> 08:01.174
Off Key, please don't go.

08:04.155 --> 08:05.895
Mr. Zhou, I love you so much!

08:06.646 --> 08:11.209
♪ You smile,
and get a little closer to me ♪

08:12.459 --> 08:14.325
♪ I want to go with you ♪

08:14.325 --> 08:17.450
♪ To a farther future ♪

08:17.450 --> 08:19.701
♪ Dreams can reach the other shore ♪

08:19.701 --> 08:23.624
♪ I really like you a lot ♪

08:23.624 --> 08:26.568
♪ The first time I am brave ♪

08:26.568 --> 08:30.152
♪ Looking up,
chasing the momentary fireworks ♪

08:30.152 --> 08:37.718
♪ Falling in the midst of summer,
every moment of falling in love. Let it blossom ♪

08:48.235 --> 08:50.495
I'm leaving now.

09:19.635 --> 09:20.735
What's wrong?

09:23.915 --> 09:28.855
I want to tell you something.

09:29.875 --> 09:30.875
Speak out.

09:32.674 --> 09:34.655
My grandpa invites you
for dinner tomorrow.

09:37.115 --> 09:40.015
- Sure!
- You agreed?

09:41.035 --> 09:42.375
Can I refuse?

09:42.954 --> 09:46.371
No! My grandpa holds
a significant position in our family.

09:46.395 --> 09:49.314
If you refuse his invitation...

09:49.314 --> 09:50.694
I didn't.

09:53.314 --> 09:56.011
However, I have outpatient appointments
at the branch hospital tomorrow.

09:56.035 --> 09:58.615
After that, I will come to pick you up.

09:59.594 --> 10:02.211
I don't have any classes next morning.
I'll come to meet you.

10:02.235 --> 10:06.334
- We'll go straight there.
- Okay.

10:07.875 --> 10:09.135
And this.

10:24.367 --> 10:26.450
(Qiang Qingci)

10:29.395 --> 10:32.775
- I'm leaving. Bye!
- Bye!

10:33.635 --> 10:37.655
Well done! Qiang Qingci. Bye!

10:48.355 --> 10:52.770
- Brother, where is Dong Yiru?
- Her idol has taken a back seat.

10:52.794 --> 10:54.574
She didn't come
due to excessive sadness.

10:56.395 --> 10:59.255
- What is it?
- It's nothing.

11:14.875 --> 11:19.535
- I put this here. Let her take it.
- Okay. Got it.

11:20.770 --> 11:24.274
(Branch of Ancheng
First People's Hospital)

11:38.594 --> 11:39.735
Come in.

11:40.714 --> 11:42.655
Dr. Mo, there's another patient.

11:46.194 --> 11:47.334
Want to see a doctor?

11:48.395 --> 11:49.535
Yeah.

11:51.794 --> 11:54.735
I'm off work now.
And I have a date with my girlfriend.

11:57.275 --> 11:58.814
Really?

11:59.875 --> 12:02.331
But I didn't get
an appointment this morning.

12:02.355 --> 12:05.170
The nurse said you'd see
dozens of patients more every day.

12:05.194 --> 12:08.131
She helped me make an appointment
and asked me to take my chances.

12:08.155 --> 12:14.054
She said it'd be up to you. If you're not
willing, I have to come next time.

12:20.594 --> 12:22.255
I'll take on one more patient.

12:23.235 --> 12:24.574
Thank you, doctor.

12:33.915 --> 12:36.255
What's wrong with you?

12:40.395 --> 12:42.535
I have multiple elder brothers.

12:45.995 --> 12:50.415
They've been protective of me since young.
They won't let me find a boyfriend.

12:53.714 --> 12:57.930
They heard my boyfriend
was coming for dinner today,

12:57.954 --> 12:59.264
so they'd all come.

12:59.264 --> 13:02.535
One of them was on a business trip
in Beijing. He has returned for this.

13:03.355 --> 13:07.731
- Really?
- Since last night,

13:07.755 --> 13:09.971
I've been particularly unwell.

13:09.995 --> 13:12.290
I've lain awake all night,
tossing and turning.

13:12.314 --> 13:16.615
This morning, my heartbeat quickened.

13:17.314 --> 13:18.855
What should I do, doctor?

13:20.755 --> 13:23.574
You're experiencing too much stress.

13:24.834 --> 13:26.015
Yes.

13:27.115 --> 13:28.934
Issues regarding meeting with parents,

13:30.355 --> 13:32.454
your boyfriend will handle it.

13:32.554 --> 13:39.694
You should eat well,
drink well and sleep well. Understand?

13:42.714 --> 13:47.690
I got it. Thank you, doctor.
You're awesome.

13:47.714 --> 13:50.211
After your words, I'm feeling better.
You healed me.

13:50.235 --> 13:52.491
- You're so brilliant.
- You are welcome.

13:52.515 --> 13:54.974
And for now,

13:55.714 --> 13:57.694
you just need to get some rest.

14:18.794 --> 14:20.294
Need an electrocardiogram?

14:28.434 --> 14:31.174
If yes, I'll write you a prescription,
and you can come in the afternoon.

14:31.714 --> 14:35.934
If not, let's go out for dinner now.

14:45.554 --> 14:48.255
Why are you standing here?
I asked you to go to Dr. Mo for signature?

14:48.834 --> 14:51.094
Dr. Mo has scheduled a meal
with this patient.

14:51.794 --> 14:52.974
Now?

15:07.594 --> 15:11.855
- So formal?
- Should I not place importance on it?

15:15.115 --> 15:16.895
- I need to change my clothes.
- Okay.

16:00.314 --> 16:03.135
- What's wrong?
- Nothing.

16:04.314 --> 16:05.375
Then let's go.

16:11.395 --> 16:13.615
- I'm not sure.
- No.

16:15.434 --> 16:18.375
- Dr. Mo, sign here.
- Okay.

16:31.354 --> 16:32.375
Okay.

16:41.035 --> 16:43.174
- Done.
- Okay.

16:48.275 --> 16:49.574
This is my girlfriend.

16:51.155 --> 16:54.051
- Dr. Mo, we'll leave you two alone.
- Let's go.

16:54.075 --> 16:56.375
- Thank you!
- His girlfriend.

17:00.555 --> 17:03.494
It's your fault. They thought
you were having a date with a patient.

17:04.915 --> 17:08.254
It's you who discredited me
by pretending to be a patient.

17:09.474 --> 17:15.214
- Do you have a good reputation?
- Without a doubt. Let's go.

17:25.434 --> 17:27.974
Isn't he here yet?

17:33.714 --> 17:36.690
Why are you so nervous?
It's her boyfriend after all.

17:36.714 --> 17:39.051
All of you left work early
and are back now.

17:39.075 --> 17:41.410
Especially the eldest brother,
who ended his business trip early.

17:41.434 --> 17:44.250
The elders are occupied with work.
As her brothers,

17:44.274 --> 17:48.615
- we must be concerned about her with this.
- Right.

17:48.875 --> 17:49.974
Jia.

17:50.835 --> 17:53.254
Adult men are a different story.

17:53.595 --> 17:57.415
As married individuals,
my brother and I understand men the best.

17:57.595 --> 18:00.571
What's most significant
is her thoughts. She likes him.

18:00.595 --> 18:04.934
- Well...
- Right. The key is she likes him.

18:06.355 --> 18:07.615
Wait a bit.

18:08.835 --> 18:10.895
There's never a parking space
available here.

18:11.595 --> 18:15.454
There is a ground-level parking lot
next to the shopping mall ahead. Go there.

18:16.915 --> 18:19.774
There are many items in the trunk.
Let's leave them here.

18:20.194 --> 18:23.974
- What items?
- Some gifts for my first visit.

18:27.194 --> 18:28.494
I am inexperienced.

18:29.434 --> 18:33.895
You park the car to the side.
I'll have them come down to collect them.

18:37.274 --> 18:43.295
- Grandpa, we're on the same side.
- Sheng. Where are you now?

18:44.795 --> 18:46.534
Is there a traffic jam?

18:47.194 --> 18:48.970
Park in my parking space.

18:48.994 --> 18:52.771
- I can move my car. Nearby...
- Brother, listen to me.

18:52.795 --> 18:56.051
Parking here is challenging.

18:56.075 --> 18:57.771
And he is a stranger here.

18:57.795 --> 18:59.194
He is bound to lose his way.

18:59.194 --> 19:01.835
- Hello?
- It's your first visit. Your mom is nervous.

19:01.835 --> 19:04.075
- She asked me to give you a call.
- We are your elder brothers.

19:04.075 --> 19:06.774
How is it going? Where are you?
Have you seen them?

19:07.075 --> 19:10.331
I'm busy.
We'll discuss it when I get back.

19:10.355 --> 19:13.115
- Stay there. I'll come to you.
- I can hardly wait.

19:13.115 --> 19:16.355
We're at the entrance of the alley.
Come out and help us with the stuff.

19:16.355 --> 19:19.210
- Hello?
- Come get the stuff. We'll talk later.

19:19.234 --> 19:21.210
Okay! We're coming now!

19:21.234 --> 19:23.534
Can't I even inquire?

19:23.835 --> 19:26.734
- Why aren't you responding?
- Okay, I got it.

19:31.474 --> 19:32.315
- Hurry up!
- What's wrong?

19:32.315 --> 19:34.891
- We need to move the items.
- Come on!

19:34.915 --> 19:37.970
- Hurry up!
- Not all of you.

19:37.994 --> 19:40.771
- Don't frighten him.
- That's right!

19:40.795 --> 19:42.034
- I will stay.
- You just got back. Stay here.

19:42.034 --> 19:43.811
- I'm not finished yet.
- I'll go with them.

19:43.835 --> 19:45.410
- Can you?
- Of course!

19:45.434 --> 19:46.274
- Okay!
- Let's go.

19:46.274 --> 19:48.771
- Come on!
- Come on!

19:48.795 --> 19:49.815
Come on!

19:51.274 --> 19:54.174
My brothers are hard to deal with.

19:55.034 --> 19:58.214
Don't smile later. Be serious.

19:59.795 --> 20:04.174
- Cheer up.
- Don't be so fiendish, second brother.

20:05.635 --> 20:09.331
- Be serious.
- They are here! Close the window.

20:09.355 --> 20:12.331
Don't go out!
They'll keep interrogating you.

20:12.355 --> 20:13.851
- Okay!
- Is this the car?

20:13.875 --> 20:15.410
- That's the car?
- Brothers.

20:15.434 --> 20:17.655
- Here.
- Over here.

20:18.315 --> 20:21.118
- Look away now. Go!
- Shouldn't we say hello?

20:21.118 --> 20:24.034
No! Go! Just move the stuff.

20:24.034 --> 20:26.135
- What are all these items?
- We can't park the car here.

20:42.514 --> 20:44.974
Buddy, nice.

20:46.075 --> 20:48.371
- Hello, brothers.
- Some goods bought you over?

20:48.395 --> 20:52.650
- Brothers, let's deal with the items.
- Get the items first.

20:52.674 --> 20:54.250
- Get them first.
- Come on.

20:54.274 --> 20:55.494
And this one.

20:56.194 --> 20:58.194
- Look away now.
- Here you are, third brother.

20:58.194 --> 20:59.835
- We must not park here.
- Look away now.

20:59.835 --> 21:01.674
- Won't he come out to help?
- He has to park the car.

21:01.674 --> 21:05.474
- What Vintage year is this wine?
- Don't gossip, second brother.

21:05.474 --> 21:08.375
Come on. Third brother. Don't gossip.

21:08.474 --> 21:09.811
We're going to park the car.

21:09.835 --> 21:13.091
You can park in my parking space.
I can move my car.

21:13.115 --> 21:15.234
- No need!
- Parking space?

21:15.234 --> 21:17.891
- Come on. Let's go.
- What's all this stuff?

21:17.915 --> 21:21.690
- Didn't he wear sunglasses?
- Second brother.

21:21.714 --> 21:24.010
- Come on.
- Third brother.

21:24.034 --> 21:27.375
- Let's go.
- Where to?

21:28.115 --> 21:30.454
The shopping mall is ahead.
There's a parking lot behind it.

21:41.315 --> 21:46.095
- They're nice, but they chatter non-stop.
- It's okay.

21:49.635 --> 21:51.174
They are here.

21:53.155 --> 21:57.534
Grandpa, this is Mo Qingcheng.

21:58.395 --> 22:00.575
Hello, Grandpa. Hello, brothers.

22:03.875 --> 22:06.734
Hello, welcome. Have a seat please.

22:09.115 --> 22:13.534
What are you guys waiting for?
Get the tea ready and cut some fruit.

22:15.795 --> 22:18.895
- What would you like to eat?
- Anything. Just go.

22:19.835 --> 22:23.010
- Dr. Mo, we are old acquaintances.
- Right, hello.

22:23.034 --> 22:24.615
Please have a seat.

22:25.395 --> 22:29.555
- It's my turn. Hello, I'm Zhao Cheng.
- Hello.

22:29.555 --> 22:31.650
- Hello, I'm Shen Yao.
- Hello.

22:31.674 --> 22:32.895
A Chinese server player.

22:35.194 --> 22:40.291
- I heard you...
- No manners. The elder has yet to speak.

22:40.315 --> 22:43.010
Dr. Mo, can we chat?

22:43.034 --> 22:44.875
- Right.
- Please have a seat.

22:44.875 --> 22:46.494
- Sit down.
- Sit down.

22:47.994 --> 22:52.210
- Grandpa.
- Did she mention it to you?

22:52.234 --> 22:55.615
- I have also been a doctor.
- Yes.

22:56.034 --> 22:58.494
Our family also has doctors.
My parents are both doctors.

22:59.795 --> 23:04.135
They are doctors. No one looked after you
when you were young, right?

23:05.355 --> 23:08.055
I'm accustomed to taking care of myself.

23:09.474 --> 23:13.174
Sheng, are you aware of this situation?

23:15.034 --> 23:18.934
I knew. However,
he seldom mentioned this.

23:20.474 --> 23:24.895
- Have you just become acquainted?
- It's been a long time.

23:26.835 --> 23:30.855
Grandpa, what is your preferred tea?

23:31.555 --> 23:35.534
- I like fresh tea.
- Excellent. So does my father.

23:35.795 --> 23:39.694
My father has instructed me
to bring you some fresh tea.

23:39.795 --> 23:41.575
- Good.
- Grandpa, have some tea.

23:41.635 --> 23:44.055
- Say thank you for me to your father.
- You're welcome.

23:45.355 --> 23:46.534
Try the tea.

23:49.754 --> 23:50.815
Be careful.

23:51.474 --> 23:53.494
Is it truly your first time?

23:54.714 --> 23:55.934
What's on your mind?

23:59.555 --> 24:03.170
What are you doing? How could you
let the guest pour me the tea?

24:03.194 --> 24:05.415
He has just taken it away.

24:05.875 --> 24:07.331
It's okay, Grandpa.

24:07.355 --> 24:09.494
- Fruit is ready.
- Where's your etiquette?

24:10.155 --> 24:12.494
- Thank you.
- Come on.

24:12.595 --> 24:14.295
- Thank you, brother.
- Please.

24:23.514 --> 24:26.930
What's wrong with you
still standing here?

24:26.954 --> 24:31.494
The guest is here.
Go shop for groceries for the dinner.

24:32.355 --> 24:34.891
- Let's go.
- Gu Jia, stay and have a chat with us.

24:34.915 --> 24:36.355
- You hear that?
- Okay, Grandpa.

24:36.355 --> 24:37.595
- You go shopping.
- You guys go!

24:37.595 --> 24:40.174
- You too.
- Me?

24:40.234 --> 24:41.555
- Come on.
- Come on.

24:41.555 --> 24:43.410
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

24:43.434 --> 24:44.754
- Go.
- Everyone?

24:44.754 --> 24:47.135
- All of you.
- Go.

24:47.674 --> 24:50.555
- You're the best, Grandpa.
- Enjoying the tea.

24:50.555 --> 24:53.250
- Thank you.
- Is there anything you cannot eat?

24:53.274 --> 24:54.494
No, brother.

24:55.674 --> 24:56.774
Thank you.

24:59.714 --> 25:01.531
- Where should we go?
- The wet market.

25:01.555 --> 25:02.655
Stop!

25:05.034 --> 25:06.690
- You'd better get back.
- What for?

25:06.714 --> 25:09.891
- To listen to what they chat about.
- Come on.

25:09.915 --> 25:11.851
- Whatever they discuss.
- What do you want?

25:11.875 --> 25:14.734
- Go. Hurry up.
- Nothing, just an undercover.

25:14.875 --> 25:17.254
- You are a deep card.
- Wait for me!

25:18.075 --> 25:19.734
At the store, I first...

25:22.514 --> 25:27.575
- Why are you back?
- They asked me to have a chat with Dr. Mo.

25:30.474 --> 25:33.295
Do you play games on usual days, Dr. Mo?

25:34.234 --> 25:36.254
I can't play games.

25:37.395 --> 25:41.450
I usually enjoy listening to music.
I used to play basketball.

25:41.474 --> 25:43.934
But now I need to protect my hands,
so I'm not playing anymore.

25:44.274 --> 25:48.855
- That's great. Sheng sings very well.
- I know.

25:49.994 --> 25:51.615
She is also a talented songwriter.

25:52.234 --> 25:54.855
We got to know each other
due to the songs she wrote.

25:55.714 --> 25:58.655
I'm one of her unknown fans.

25:58.994 --> 26:02.131
That's right. I've heard it online.

26:02.155 --> 26:06.250
Lovers who appreciate each other
can last a long time.

26:06.274 --> 26:08.611
Lovers should appreciate each other.

26:08.635 --> 26:13.415
- She is young, but she is talented.
- Yes.

26:14.155 --> 26:15.534
More accomplished than me.

26:16.315 --> 26:21.575
Dr. Mo, I'd like to share with you a song
that Sheng has recently composed.

26:22.234 --> 26:26.571
Grandpa, I'll take him
upstairs for a tour.

26:26.595 --> 26:27.895
Okay.

26:28.555 --> 26:31.135
I was in a good chat with Dr. Mo.

26:32.434 --> 26:34.291
Grandpa, we're heading upstairs now.

26:34.315 --> 26:38.450
- Take it easy. Feel at home.
- Okay.

26:38.474 --> 26:40.234
Dr. Mo, may I friend you on WeChat?
We can play games together.

26:40.234 --> 26:42.210
- I will learn to play games from you.
- Okay.

26:42.234 --> 26:44.690
- Sit down.
- Are you polite?

26:44.714 --> 26:46.650
- Was I wrong?
- It's his first visit here.

26:46.674 --> 26:49.410
Don't talk such rot!
Go away and play your games!

26:49.434 --> 26:52.571
- Have you been living here since young?
- More or less.

26:52.595 --> 26:55.450
Ever since my grandma passed away,
my brothers took turns to live here.

26:55.474 --> 26:59.254
I moved here after junior high school.
This way.

27:04.234 --> 27:06.694
This is my grandpa's room.

27:08.595 --> 27:11.135
This is my room.

27:14.954 --> 27:16.055
Can I come in?

27:19.434 --> 27:20.895
Such a cozy room!

27:26.835 --> 27:29.335
- This is you in childhood?
- Right.

27:31.274 --> 27:32.895
This is where you compose music?

27:32.954 --> 27:35.375
All of my songs were composed here.

27:46.795 --> 27:48.095
What are you looking at?

27:49.954 --> 27:52.855
I would like to know
about your sight from here.

27:53.875 --> 27:56.534
Just the streets and residents.

28:06.835 --> 28:09.335
I have had this piano
since I was five years old.

28:11.434 --> 28:14.051
You've taken good care of it.
You must not have been practicing hard.

28:14.075 --> 28:17.214
I practice every day.

28:18.915 --> 28:24.895
You told many lies just now.
You're not one of my fans.

28:25.555 --> 28:27.415
They could be too easily found out.

28:28.915 --> 28:31.254
Some are true and some are false.

28:33.274 --> 28:35.055
All false.

28:37.115 --> 28:38.174
Not really.

28:39.674 --> 28:43.815
- Alright, let's go upstairs.
- Okay.

28:53.075 --> 28:54.774
Be careful.

28:55.595 --> 28:56.855
You first.

28:59.034 --> 29:03.174
Nice. The small courtyard upstairs
is quite cozy.

29:03.315 --> 29:05.734
I often jumped rope here
when I was young.

29:06.795 --> 29:10.135
Anyway, it's your house downstairs,
so no one's likely to complain.

29:10.474 --> 29:14.418
No complaints.
But someone called the police.

29:14.846 --> 29:16.055
So serious?

29:16.514 --> 29:18.930
Once I gained a bit of weight
and wanted to lose it.

29:18.954 --> 29:21.410
I couldn't fall asleep at night,
so I climbed up here and jumped rope.

29:21.434 --> 29:24.615
I felt quite tired after more than 100 jumps.

29:25.194 --> 29:29.091
I was pacing back and forth
and enjoying the scenery here.

29:29.115 --> 29:31.371
Then, the newly arrived neighbor
called the police.

29:31.395 --> 29:33.174
He assumed I was contemplating suicide.

29:38.434 --> 29:41.811
- Female crab.
- You're not skilled in cooking.

29:41.835 --> 29:44.891
Crabs are not easy to cook.

29:44.915 --> 29:48.534
What are you talking about?
Grandpa likes it. Right, Grandpa?

29:48.875 --> 29:53.335
Forget it. Wait for Sheng's mother
to come back to cook it.

29:53.395 --> 29:56.091
I'll hire a cook later to deal with it.

29:56.115 --> 29:59.291
- You're too arrogant.
- All female crabs.

29:59.315 --> 30:00.895
Brothers.

30:02.875 --> 30:05.895
Brothers, let me try.

30:06.754 --> 30:08.014
You?

30:08.994 --> 30:10.335
You can cook?

30:11.315 --> 30:13.494
I learned a bit because my family
likes to eat crabs.

30:16.155 --> 30:18.415
This dish is challenging to prepare.

30:18.915 --> 30:22.534
Indeed. So, I just said I'd try it.

30:24.915 --> 30:27.974
Okay, we will wait for the meal.

30:28.954 --> 30:30.174
Take this for me.

30:33.994 --> 30:37.131
Sheng, Dr. Mo is working hard.

30:37.155 --> 30:39.851
He is trying
to conquer our family this evening.

30:39.875 --> 30:42.694
Just wait for the meal.
Take this and hang it outside.

30:42.954 --> 30:44.131
- I...
- Go.

30:44.155 --> 30:46.490
- Be careful with your hands.
- Brother.

30:46.514 --> 30:49.155
What are you doing here? Get out.

30:49.155 --> 30:50.835
- Can you?
- I will assist him.

30:50.835 --> 30:51.994
- Cook the rice.
- So do you, eldest brother.

30:51.994 --> 30:54.434
- Take care, both of you.
- Bye. Yes, don't worry.

30:54.434 --> 30:56.335
- The vegetables haven't been washed.
- Bye.

30:58.115 --> 31:00.135
It's your specialty.

31:01.714 --> 31:03.415
Only this one?

31:06.555 --> 31:08.194
Will they search for recipes?

31:08.194 --> 31:11.694
It's not easy to instantly
master and apply. Let's wait.

31:12.355 --> 31:15.254
Grandpa is a master of local cuisine.
He's really picky.

31:15.754 --> 31:18.934
He might just be in the line of fire.

31:19.034 --> 31:21.974
- Let's go.
- Grandpa, someone is preparing the meal.

31:35.994 --> 31:37.415
Pass me some flour.

31:57.994 --> 32:01.815
I forgot to tell you
I prefer thin strips of rice cake.

32:02.635 --> 32:07.095
It's okay. This is for stir-frying.
I'll cut into strips for you later.

33:06.234 --> 33:09.055
I'm cooking. It's hot here.

33:09.434 --> 33:14.371
This is too easy for you.
I have to add something for you.

33:14.395 --> 33:16.254
I'm increasing the difficulty for you.

33:18.274 --> 33:20.135
Hurry up and focus your attention.

33:33.714 --> 33:36.375
- Does it smell good?
- It smells good.

33:43.635 --> 33:45.254
The crabs are ready.

33:48.514 --> 33:52.135
- It looks nice.
- Grandpa, try it later.

33:52.835 --> 33:55.734
- Good cooking.
- The smell is good. Have a try.

33:56.155 --> 33:58.534
- Have you washed your hands?
- Let's try it.

33:58.715 --> 34:00.195
Sheng, let's go to the kitchen
to help him.

34:00.195 --> 34:03.275
No need. Just set the table.
We'll eat soon.

34:03.275 --> 34:04.235
Really?

34:04.235 --> 34:06.371
There's no need.
He's already working on the next dish.

34:06.395 --> 34:08.534
Don't complicate matters.

34:09.315 --> 34:11.651
Okay! Let's set the table.

34:11.675 --> 34:13.275
- Right!
- Take the stools.

34:13.275 --> 34:15.014
Looks pretty good.

34:15.675 --> 34:18.275
Stewed pomfret is ready.

34:18.275 --> 34:20.815
- So fast?
- He is a quick cook.

34:21.954 --> 34:23.895
This fish looks tasty.

34:24.434 --> 34:26.514
- Sauteed alfalfa with rice wine.
- Another one?

34:26.514 --> 34:28.375
Shrimps with scallion oil.

34:29.154 --> 34:30.930
I like this one.

34:30.954 --> 34:32.534
- The fourth.
- Okay.

34:32.634 --> 34:34.215
Move the zizania there.

34:35.395 --> 34:38.691
- Baked gluten and mutton pot.
- Here, give them to me.

34:38.715 --> 34:40.014
Be careful.

34:41.275 --> 34:43.891
You just let the guest
work alone in the kitchen?

34:43.915 --> 34:46.211
Sheng prevents us from entering.

34:46.235 --> 34:49.014
Yes. Grandpa. Sheng chased us out.

34:50.715 --> 34:52.154
Apart from my aunt and grandpa,

34:52.154 --> 34:56.775
I've never seen anyone who can prepare
such a large table of local cuisine.

34:56.994 --> 34:58.970
Sheng is truly fortunate.

34:58.994 --> 35:02.771
Not only can her mother cook,
but her boyfriend is also a chef.

35:02.795 --> 35:04.114
- You're really talkative.
- I'll start with this.

35:04.114 --> 35:05.295
Don't move.

35:06.114 --> 35:08.415
I'll go and prepare the rice.

35:18.235 --> 35:20.054
Serve the rice.

35:21.434 --> 35:23.255
He's performing well.

35:23.954 --> 35:25.094
Just go out.

35:26.835 --> 35:28.450
We will wash in a moment.

35:28.474 --> 35:31.855
- If you stay longer, I'll starve.
- Okay!

35:35.715 --> 35:39.610
Let's raise our glasses
and welcome Dr. Mo here to visit.

35:39.634 --> 35:42.171
- Welcome.
- Thank you.

35:42.195 --> 35:45.811
I'm also very happy to meet grandpa
and the brothers this time.

35:45.835 --> 35:47.215
Cheers!

35:51.795 --> 35:53.891
I didn't expect
you took charge of cooking

35:53.915 --> 35:56.594
on your first visit to our home.
We didn't treat you well, Dr. Mo.

35:56.594 --> 35:58.410
It's my honor.

35:58.434 --> 36:02.090
Sheng is the only daughter
in our family.

36:02.114 --> 36:04.934
We have been shielding her
since her childhood.

36:05.154 --> 36:08.675
- So, we're a bit harsh on boys.
- Yes.

36:08.675 --> 36:12.291
It's for this reason
that she has only now found a boyfriend.

36:12.315 --> 36:16.855
- What kind of talk is that?
- I didn't have anyone I liked before.

36:17.835 --> 36:21.614
Now you've encountered Dr. Mo
whom you like.

36:24.594 --> 36:28.054
- Grandpa, try some. He cooked them.
- Okay.

36:33.395 --> 36:35.934
Quite impressive, almost matching mine.

36:36.634 --> 36:39.371
Not even close. I hope to learn more
from you in the future.

36:39.395 --> 36:40.915
- Come often in the future.
- Okay.

36:40.915 --> 36:42.275
- Come on.
- Come on.

36:42.275 --> 36:44.691
- Come on.
- Have a taste.

36:44.715 --> 36:46.074
Have a taste. I believe it's quite good.

36:46.074 --> 36:49.610
I want to try a vegetable dish.
Vegetable dishes require skills.

36:49.634 --> 36:53.171
This is absolutely delicious.
Can you tell me how to make it?

36:53.195 --> 36:55.415
- Okay.
- It's absolutely delicious.

36:56.594 --> 36:59.610
- It's really good.
- Here. Welcome, Dr. Mo.

36:59.634 --> 37:01.695
- Welcome.
- Thank you.

37:02.835 --> 37:05.134
- This meat is truly excellent.
- So soft and well-done.

37:05.434 --> 37:08.934
- I'm glad you like them.
- The cooking time is well-controlled.

37:09.474 --> 37:11.651
- Not bad.
- Learn from it.

37:11.675 --> 37:14.974
- This takes a long time to stew.
- Stop gaming and hurry up.

37:17.675 --> 37:19.175
You'll never learn, anyway.

37:34.514 --> 37:38.295
- I want to introduce you to someone.
- Who?

37:38.554 --> 37:41.815
You've met her,
but she doesn't know who you are.

37:43.474 --> 37:45.094
Okay.

37:53.554 --> 37:57.454
- Welcome.
- Welcome. You're here.

37:58.114 --> 37:59.295
Yiru.

38:00.875 --> 38:02.454
Boyfriend?

38:03.034 --> 38:05.434
Let me introduce you. He is...

38:05.434 --> 38:08.970
I know. Dr. Mo, the young talent
from the hospital across the street.

38:08.994 --> 38:11.494
A frequent customer here. I know.

38:15.195 --> 38:18.574
Hello, I'm Qiang Qingci.

38:30.235 --> 38:34.371
We've met a few times in the past,
but I never told you my stage name.

38:34.395 --> 38:37.614
- Because...
- I know.

38:37.755 --> 38:42.450
Upon recognition,
it would disrupt your regular work.

38:42.474 --> 38:44.375
I know.

38:47.235 --> 38:53.891
I heard
you were going to take a back seat.

38:53.915 --> 38:56.154
I thought you were quite pitiful.

38:56.154 --> 38:58.315
Moreover, Sheng has a new boyfriend.

38:58.315 --> 39:01.651
How upset you will be. Sheng.

39:01.675 --> 39:05.114
You two are really a couple now. Sheng.

39:05.114 --> 39:08.090
- Calm down.
- I can't hold it.

39:08.114 --> 39:11.114
I noticed the poster
you left for me this morning.

39:11.114 --> 39:13.175
I was quite upset.

39:13.755 --> 39:16.775
She reserved that poster for you?

39:17.154 --> 39:21.094
Of course, who else could it be?

39:22.235 --> 39:26.494
- Am I considered a family member?
- Of course.

39:27.634 --> 39:30.050
I accidentally became a family member.

39:30.074 --> 39:32.775
I'll treat you some snacks.

39:33.554 --> 39:37.050
- Hold on a minute.
- Get some more. We'll head to the studio.

39:37.074 --> 39:39.275
I'll bring everything for you.

39:39.275 --> 39:41.211
Take all of them. It's on me.

39:41.235 --> 39:43.610
No way. It shall be on me.

39:43.634 --> 39:46.010
If you regard me as a friend,
then let me pay.

39:46.034 --> 39:49.175
- Okay, then.
- Okay.

39:49.275 --> 39:52.331
- Thank you on behalf of everyone.
- Nah, it's not a big deal.

39:52.355 --> 39:54.614
We are all good friends.

39:55.154 --> 39:57.450
Take some snacks you like.

39:57.474 --> 39:59.335
I know.

40:01.922 --> 40:03.514
(Wangjia Supermarket)

40:03.514 --> 40:06.142
- Okay. It's enough.
- It's enough. Yiru.

40:06.142 --> 40:07.534
- It's enough.
- Okay.

40:19.707 --> 40:23.058
(Weibo of Qiang Qingci's fans)

40:25.877 --> 40:30.162
(Congratulations on your retirement,
Mr. Qiang.)

40:32.514 --> 40:34.675
Your table manners.
I don't know what to say.

40:34.675 --> 40:35.851
- Add some nuts.
- No.

40:35.875 --> 40:38.251
- Adding nuts enhances the taste.
- Nuts are delicious.

40:38.275 --> 40:39.735
He doesn't know it.

40:51.315 --> 40:52.654
What are you looking at?

40:54.154 --> 40:57.410
Those artworks created
by the limners for you.

40:57.434 --> 41:02.090
I planned to create a photo album
for you as a memento.

41:02.114 --> 41:05.654
However, your fans love you more than me.
They are already making it.

41:47.675 --> 41:48.934
It's rum flavor.

41:49.994 --> 41:54.054
My favorite flavor. Rum is a spirit.

41:54.154 --> 41:55.610
I remember the first time I tasted it.

41:55.634 --> 41:59.574
I thought it would be quite odd
to combine it with milk.

41:59.634 --> 42:04.375
But it turned out to be delicious.
Sweet milk plus wine and red grapes.

42:04.594 --> 42:07.815
What a brilliant recipe!

42:15.994 --> 42:20.054
Your voice is perfect
for ice cream commercials.

42:21.994 --> 42:25.534
I've done some before,
just not this flavor.

42:26.275 --> 42:31.895
You must be so confused,
having voiced so many commercials.

42:33.795 --> 42:36.094
I still remember them.

42:38.034 --> 42:43.134
Being at the top in voice acting,
all good resources are for you.

42:43.275 --> 42:45.574
Do you have any thoughts to share?

42:50.195 --> 42:55.375
As a perfectionist,
I experience significant pressure.

42:58.315 --> 43:03.054
So many eyes
are watching you with anticipation.

43:03.954 --> 43:09.731
Being the same is lagging behind.
Each work should progress slightly.

43:09.755 --> 43:14.094
Otherwise,
I cannot even convince myself.

43:21.915 --> 43:24.454
Mr. Qiang, go for it!

43:59.777 --> 44:01.758
♪ Beyond the ferry bridge ♪

44:01.758 --> 44:07.816
♪ Fragrant grass spreading
across the eternal mountain ♪

44:08.309 --> 44:10.246
♪ Dream gone ♪

44:10.246 --> 44:15.946
♪ Geese come and go,
mountain changes to river ♪

44:16.842 --> 44:20.414
♪ I've believed
that this life was all a dream ♪

44:20.414 --> 44:25.309
♪ Geese come and go,
mountain changes to river ♪

44:25.333 --> 44:27.414
♪ Among old friends ♪

44:27.414 --> 44:29.535
♪ It's easy to encounter ♪

44:29.559 --> 44:32.830
♪ Hard to part ♪

44:32.830 --> 44:36.959
♪ The spring wind parts the Milky Way
with a single sound ♪

44:36.959 --> 44:41.275
♪ Why farewell guests
until the deep of night ♪

44:41.275 --> 44:46.022
♪ I head to the northwest,
you to the southeast ♪

44:46.782 --> 44:51.998
♪ Wind rises on the willow shore ♪

44:51.998 --> 44:54.634
♪ It's like going to the feast ♪

44:54.634 --> 45:00.527
♪ Life is just like going to a feast ♪

45:00.527 --> 45:03.069
♪ Dreams come and go ♪

45:03.071 --> 45:09.050
♪ Dreams fade
like the end of a feast upon waking ♪

45:09.050 --> 45:13.401
♪ The pavilion is parting,
the mountain is solitary ♪

45:13.401 --> 45:17.951
♪ We can see the bright moon
at the same time ♪

45:17.951 --> 45:20.446
♪ No need to ask about the foggy waters ♪

45:20.446 --> 45:26.339
♪ Which boat am I on ♪

45:28.213 --> 45:30.215
♪ It's like going to the feast ♪

45:30.302 --> 45:34.642
♪ Life is just like going to a feast ♪

45:35.612 --> 45:37.572
♪ Dreams come and go ♪

45:38.174 --> 45:42.674
♪ Dreams fade
like the end of a feast upon waking ♪

45:44.501 --> 45:48.594
♪ The pavilion is parting,
the mountain is solitary ♪

45:49.653 --> 45:54.034
♪ We can see the bright moon
at the same time ♪

45:54.997 --> 45:57.296
♪ Boundless foggy waters ♪

45:57.589 --> 46:01.860
♪ Just like you seeing me back ♪
